(LaST POST FOR TONIGHT. CYA ALL TOMORROW ON MONDAY MORNING)


::Feline::

She looked around and heard voices.  She turned and went away from 
the voices, looking around amd mapping it all inher memory banks.  
She noticed that no one had found her yet, but she didn't want push 
her luck.  She went back the way she came and went back up the 
stairs.  She would try to get a tour of hte ship later on.  She 
started wandering about and was accidentily headed to the bridge.
